I stayed on the force! You left!

728
00:56:08,580 --> 00:56:10,017
你在改寫歷史
You're rewriting history!

729
00:56:10,615 --> 00:56:12,714
我退休了 我沒有放棄
I retired. I didn't quit!

730
00:56:12,716 --> 00:56:14,283
夥計們 別鬧了
You guys, knock it off!

731
00:56:14,285 --> 00:56:17,149
你求我回來 我回來了
You begged me to get back! I came back!

732
00:56:18,589 --> 00:56:20,855
從那時起 我就和你在一起
And I've been with you ever since.

733
00:56:20,857 --> 00:56:22,825
我很高興
And I'm glad. I am.

734
00:56:22,827 --> 00:56:24,826
我在這裏沒有遺憾
I have no regrets here.

735
00:56:25,966 --> 00:56:28,300
我不後悔回來
I have no regrets about being back.

736
00:56:32,736 --> 00:56:35,638
聽著 威爾
Listen, Will.

737
00:56:35,640 --> 00:56:36,875
聽我說
Listen to me.

738
00:56:39,910 --> 00:56:43,678
我知道抓住這傢伙對你來說意味著什麼
I know how much it means to you to catch this guy.

739
00:56:43,680 --> 00:56:45,010
我知道
I know that.

740
00:56:46,283 --> 00:56:48,847
我自己也這麼覺得
And, I feel like that myself.

741
00:56:49,620 --> 00:56:50,785
你明白?
You understand?

742
00:56:50,787 --> 00:56:52,654
我愛傑西卡
I loved Jessica...

743
00:56:53,602 --> 00:56:55,437
就像她是我的孩子
like she was my child.

744
00:56:55,792 --> 00:56:56,894
你知道的
You know that.

745
00:57:00,932 --> 00:57:03,299
抱歉 夥計 我
Sorry, man. I...

746
00:57:03,301 --> 00:57:05,935
我們會找到他的 你明白我在說什麼嗎?
We're gonna find this guy. You understand what I'm saying?

747
00:57:05,937 --> 00:57:08,337
我搞砸了 夥計 我搞砸了 對不起
I messed up, man. I messed up. I'm sorry.

748
00:57:08,339 --> 00:57:11,376
我們會找到他的 我向你保證
We're gonna find him. I promise you that.

749
00:57:14,879 --> 00:57:18,417
我們有什麼?
Well, what have we got here?

750
00:57:24,988 --> 00:57:28,790
緊急插播新聞
Right now we're breaking into your regular programming for this emergency report.

751
00:57:28,792 --> 00:57:31,727
據說門羅有個連環殺手逍遙法外
We're told there's a serial killer loose in Monroe.

752
00:57:31,729 --> 00:57:33,995
最令人震驚的連環殺手之一
One of the most shocking serial killers.

753
00:57:33,997 --> 00:57:35,730
居民生活在恐懼中
Residents are living in fear,

754
00:57:35,732 --> 00:57:38,033
有另一起可怕的發現
as another gruesome discovery has been made.

755
00:57:38,035 --> 00:57:40,803
警方正在尋找被絞死的受害者
Police are finding victims hung by a noose...

756
00:57:40,805 --> 00:57:44,740
門羅有個連環殺手逍遙法外 11頻道全面報導
There's a serial killer loose in Monroe. Full story at eleven.

757
00:57:44,742 --> 00:57:47,442
屍體刻字 公眾稱殺手為劊子手
...carved in the bodies. The public is dubbing the killer the Hangman.

758
00:57:47,444 --> 00:57:49,812
關掉那玩意
Let's turn that shit off.

759
00:57:49,814 --> 00:57:52,452
我們有什麼?
Okay. What do we got?

760
00:57:53,618 --> 00:57:56,999
法醫還在刮痕跡
Well, Forensics are still scraping the tracks.

761
00:57:58,089 --> 00:57:59,988
他們不會有太多的發現
You know they're not coming up with much.

762
00:57:59,990 --> 00:58:02,892
實驗室報告來了
The lab reports came in.

763
00:58:02,894 --> 00:58:04,826
襯衫上什麼都沒有
There's nothing on the shirt.

764
00:58:05,367 --> 00:58:06,567
血?DNA?
Blood? DNA?

765
