都是受害者的
Victim's.

766
00:58:08,098 --> 00:58:10,665
肯定有什麼東西 值得更多測試
Well, there must be something. Let's run some more tests.

767
00:58:10,667 --> 00:58:12,435
什麼都沒有 沒有纖維
There's nothing. There's no fibers,

768
00:58:12,437 --> 00:58:14,406
沒有動物的毛髮
there's no animal hair... there's nothing.

769
00:58:16,908 --> 00:58:18,277
你要去哪?
Where you going?

770
00:58:20,997 --> 00:58:24,543
我們還有不到30分鐘
We have less than 30 minutes! Okay?

771
00:58:24,749 --> 00:58:27,049
今晚沒人回家 繼續工作
Nobody goes home tonight! Keep working!

772
00:58:27,051 --> 00:58:28,672
發現點什麼
Find something!

773
00:58:30,921 --> 00:58:32,968
你沒有休息過?
I take it you didn't get any rest?

774
00:58:33,790 --> 00:58:35,024
沒有 你呢?
No. You?

775
00:58:35,026 --> 00:58:38,397
我從不休息
I don't rest. Ever.

776
00:58:42,834 --> 00:58:44,421
這鬼遊戲
This damn game.

777
00:58:45,836 --> 00:58:49,437
每個場景都有下一個受害者的線索 但這次沒有
Every scene has a lead to the next vic. But this one, I just can't see it.

778
00:58:49,439 --> 00:58:52,073
他在耍我們 魯內
Well, I think he's just messing with us, Ruiney.

779
00:58:52,075 --> 00:58:54,306
我們在鐵道上比他聰明
We outsmarted him at the track.

780
00:58:55,350 --> 00:58:58,435
你比他聰明 提前了時間
You outsmarted him. Got ahead of the timeline.

781
00:58:59,015 --> 00:59:02,151
火車會發現那輛車 已經來不及阻止他了
Tide would have revealed that car when it was too late to stop him.

782
00:59:02,153 --> 00:59:05,620
