我不知道為什麼
I don't know why.

879
01:07:36,165 --> 01:07:38,836
我不知道他為什麼這麼在乎
I don't know why he cared so much.

880
01:07:44,908 --> 01:07:47,177
他找到那傢伙了
But he did. He found him. He found the guy.

881
01:07:50,580 --> 01:07:52,093
